oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Johnny Darrell Press Release: Version 1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Darrell, Johnny, 1940-1997; Moeller Talent, Inc.; Offset printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white negative advertising Johnny Darrell and containing a biography of his life and accomplishments. The press release describes how Darrell taught himself to play the guitar, his music career, and personal life. The portion of the negative that would have contained a photograph of Johnny Darrell has been cut out and is missing. The negative would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
